{"tid":210863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佛家中人係咪多數都好貪心？","createTime":"2017-04-21T08:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T09:25:10.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3fe6cc313489aa9ef5c06c41a610bab7813ec8af","tid":210863,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:52:16.000Z","msg":"荃灣芙蓉山虛雲和尚紀念堂於80年代加建圍牆防範盜賊，侵佔了毗鄰地皮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;紀念堂早前入稟申請逆權侵佔毗鄰地皮部份業權。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n案件今提訊時，法官一度提及自己任執業大律師時，也曾代表芙蓉山另一間寺廟打官司，「唔知你哋佛家地方點解咁多官司？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n代表紀念堂的和尚回答說：「貪心囉！」"},{"pid":"b120b3789c09f717781de395eca610127dd2322e","tid":210863,"uid":75533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:24:59.000Z","msg":"你咪貪心囉 偷post狗"},{"pid":"419b5816935977bceb5a634bd0e34d01d2f2fcff","tid":210863,"uid":75533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T09:25:10.000Z","msg":"垃圾狗一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}